text: Richard Murray (1831-21 November 1861) was an Australian cricketer. He played four first-class matches for New South Wales between 1855-56 and 1859-60. ==See also== * List of New South Wales representative cricketers ==References== ==External links== * Category:1831 births Category:1861 deaths Category:Australian cricketers Category:New South Wales cricketers Category:Cricketers from Sydney
